## Output instructions

Return your result using the structured `PlanningCollectorResult` schema. Do NOT write files, create documents, or use terminal/Edit/Write tools. Express all decisions through structured output fields:

- `finalizedTickets` — list of `PlanningTicket` objects (ticketId, title, description, tasks, dependencies, acceptanceCriteria, effortEstimate, priority)
- `dependencyGraph` — list of `TicketDependency` objects describing ordering constraints
- `consolidatedOutput` — human-readable summary
- `collectorDecision` — routing decision (decisionType, requestedPhase, rationale)

